1. download brew if not have it
2. brew install mongodb
    mongo to find the version
3. brew services start => start mongodb
4. install node
    node -v  to find the version
5. go to folder
6. npm init-y
    gets the package.json
7. npm install graphql-yoga (graphql server)
8. create index.js
9. to iniciate node index.js
10. install mongoose
11. install material-ui or boorstrap
